THE

BERTRAND RUSSELL

SOCIETY 2023 Annual Meeting

This summer, June 16-18, 2023, the Bertrand Russell Society will hold its 50th Annual Meeting at The Universisty of Iowa, in Iowa City, Iowa. The meeting program is posted below. Abstracts of talks will be posted as soon as they are available.

All talks (and, if possible, meetings) will be presented in hybrid format. Most presenters will be in person at the University of Iowa, but some will be online. Each presentation will be 20 minutes long, with 10 minutes for questions and discussion.

Those wishing to attend the meeting can do so either in person or online. All times are Central Daylight Time, U.S. The Zoom link for attending the meeting online is:
